OL,3,CFarming brothers fined over failings
OL,4,Cthat led to cows trampling teacher to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FTwo farmers have been fined after a
OL,8,Fdeputy head teacher was killed by
OL,9,Ftheir cows while he exercised his dogs
OL,10,Fin North Yorkshire.
OL,12,FIn September 2020, David Clark, 59,
OL,13,Fwas on a public right of way while
OL,14,Frunning with his dogs in Richmond.
OL,15,FAfter being surrounded by cattle, he
OL,16,Fwas then struck to the ground.
