OL,3,CFarming brothers fined over failings
OL,4,Cthat led to cows trampling teacher to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FWitnesses reported that one of the
OL,8,Fcows then turned back and ran towards
OL,9,Fthe father-of-three, causing a fatal
OL,10,Fblow to his chest. He died at the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,14,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that
OL,15,Fbrothers Andrew and David Turnbull
OL,16,Ffailed to put up signs alerting the
OL,17,Fpublic to an alternative route across
OL,18,Ftheir field in Coalsgarth Valley,
OL,19,FNorth Yorkshire.
