OL,7,FThe brothers, of Low Gingerfield Farm,
OL,8,FRichmond, North Yorkshire, were
OL,9,Fsentenced at Teesside Crown Court on
OL,10,FMonday (3 March) after they admitted a
OL,11,Fbreach of the Health and Safety at
OL,12,FWork Act, the HSE said.
OL,14,FAndrew Turnbull, 57, was fined #1,589
OL,15,Fand ordered to pay #1,500 in costs,
OL,16,Fwhile David Turnbull, 61, was fined
OL,17,F#1,390 and ordered to pay #1,500 in
OL,18,Fcosts.
