OL,3,CFarming brothers fined over failings
OL,4,Cthat led to cows trampling teacher to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAfter the hearing, HSE inspector
OL,8,FElliot Archer said: "Andrew and David
OL,9,FTurnbull failed to do all that was
OL,10,Freasonably practicable to prevent
OL,11,Fmembers of the public being put at
OL,12,Frisk by their cattle.
OL,14,F"Farmers, landowners and other
OL,15,Flivestock keepers need to be aware of
OL,16,Fthe risk their cattle pose to members
OL,17,Fof the public and take suitable
OL,18,Fprotective and preventative measures
OL,19,Fto mitigate that risk."
