OL,3,CFarming brothers fined over failings
OL,4,Cthat led to cows trampling teacher to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe HSE advises farmers to assess the
OL,8,Frisks posed by cattle to footpath
OL,9,Fusers and to implement protective or
OL,10,Fpreventative measures.
OL,12,FThey also advise the public visiting
OL,13,Fthe countryside to give livestock
OL,14,Fplenty of space and to keep dogs under
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,FThey also advise people with dogs to
OL,18,Frelease them if you feel threatened by
OL,19,Flivestock as letting their pet go will
OL,20,Fmake it easier for both to reach
OL,21,Fsafety.
