OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Clark was deputy head of Richmond
OL,8,FSchool and, after his death, the head
OL,9,FJenna Porter called him the "heart and
OL,10,Fsoul of the school".
OL,12,FShe said in 2020: "He was an enormous
OL,13,Fcharacter, a brilliant school leader
OL,14,Fand simply a lovely man who enriched
OL,15,Fthe life of everyone he came into
OL,16,Fcontact with, just by being himself
OL,17,Fand doing what he did every day."
